Enum Class TileType

nz.ac.wgtn.swen225.lc.domain.TileType
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<TileType>, Constable
public enum TileType extends Enum<TileType>
Enum for the different types of tile in-game. Used for quick checking of a tile's type without instanceof calls.
